  <h1>Practice Page</h1>

  <p>This page contains links to areas that are meant to offer specific bits of functionality. The page also contains some minimal functionality of its own. The point of the practice page is simply allow you to play around with certain common aspects of web development.</p>

  <p>The linked-to functionality in the list below is, in some cases, stolen almost directly from <a href="http://the-internet.herokuapp.com/">The Internet</a>, usually with a few simple additions of my own.</p>

